# Steps for creating a scss script 

Created a new folder 0x03-sass_scss

Installed SASS in my local machine by running the command: 
" $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash"""
after successfully installing SASS, I ran the command:
"exit" to close my terminal and opened a new terminal.

